You can download **Scalate** from the [Snapshot Maven Repository](http://repo.fusesource.com/nexus/content/repositories/snapshots/) in the [{project_name:} area](http://repo.fusesource.com/nexus/content/repositories/snapshots/org/fusesource/scalate/).

