<div class="left" markdown="1">
# Maven
</div>
<div class="right" markdown="1">
If you build your project using [Maven](http://maven.apache.org/) then just add the following to your *pom.xml*
</div> 
<div class="right">
{coderay:: xml}<dependency>
  <groupId>org.fusesource.{project_id:}</groupId>
  <artifactId>{project_id:}-core</artifactId>
  <version>${{project_id:}-version}</version>  
</dependency>
{coderay}
</div>
<div class="right" markdown="1">
You should ensure you have the Scalate Snapshot Maven repository defined in your *pom.xml*</div> 
<div class="right">
{coderay:: xml}  <repositories>
   <repository>
     <id>fusesource.snapshots</id>
     <name>FuseSource Snapshot Repository</name>
     <url>http://repo.fusesource.com/nexus/content/repositories/snapshots</url>
     <snapshots>
       <enabled>false</enabled>
     </snapshots>
     <releases>
       <enabled>true</enabled>
     </releases>
   </repository>
 </repositories>
{coderay}
</div>


